{"tid":2409725,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"長實21 BORRETT ROAD「天池屋」呎售13.6萬 亞洲新高","createTime":"2021-02-16T04:58:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T05:20:19.000Z","uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8aaa4b026bc3225e6d0faf1d5a1139e5963242e0","tid":2409725,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T04:58:10.000Z","msg":"踏入牛年股樓齊旺，長實(1113)旗下西半山波老道21 BORRETT ROAD，剛錄得首宗成交，一伙頂層特色戶以近4.6億元沽出，呎價高達13.6萬元，打低山頂Mount Nicholson，登上全亞洲最貴分層呎價樓王寶座。<br />\n<br />\n據一手住宅物業成交紀錄冊，21 BORRETT ROAD的23樓01室「天池屋」，實用面積3,378方呎，五房間隔，另連2,131方呎天台，天台設有私人泳池，前庭717方呎，透過招標售出，昨天大年初四以4.59408億元連3個車位售出，呎價13.6萬元，打破山頂Mount Nicholson於2017年造出每呎13.21萬元舊紀錄，貴絕亞洲分層戶。<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，買家在簽訂臨時買賣合約須支付樓價5%，再於30天及120天內各支付樓價5%，餘款須於270天內付清。發展商另提供廚房廚櫃優惠。<br />\n<br />\n2017年11月，Mount Nicholson12樓C及D室以11.65億元售出，平均呎價13.21萬元，登上全亞洲最貴分層呎價樓王寶座。事隔超過3年，亞洲樓王再度換位，並將紀錄略為推高3%。"},{"pid":"8d1f650d3e021721879b11ea7e062d05c75bbaa4","tid":2409725,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T04:58:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210216/UB2HURIEHVCI7GMWLX4Y2RBNRY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210216%2FUB2HURIEHVCI7GMWLX4Y2RBNRY%2F&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2BiWBa%2BgBXVTVyFCVgu0cTpM%3D&h=647cf1de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210216%2FUB2HURIEHVCI7GMWLX4Y2RBNRY%2F&h=3b08f861\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210216/UB2HURIEHVCI7GMWLX4Y2RBNRY/</a>"},{"pid":"2c79754c004f456a6d04eb64f687e430f3b3d83a","tid":2409725,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T04:58:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f36e60d1706ce0c4d10671b5616ae14bcd95ddc","tid":2409725,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:00:44.000Z","msg":"呢類頂層單位有冇裝修？  買得起應該都會自己再裝